#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
When you view a patron's record, you will see the following fields (assuming your
account sufficient rights to at least view them):
<ul>
<li><a href="field-Patron-Patron.cgi">Patron name</a>
<li><a href="field_Patron_Distributor.cgi">Distributor</a>
<li><a href="field_Patron_Route.cgi">Route</a>
<li><a href="field_Patron_Email.cgi">Email</a>
<li><a href="field_Patron_Phone.cgi">Phone</a>
<li><a href="field_Patron_Notify.cgi">Notify</a>
<li><a href="field_Patron_Address.cgi">Address</a>
<li><a href="field_Patron_Coords.cgi">Coords</a>
<li><a href="field_Patron_Status.cgi">Status</a>
<li><a href="field-Patron-Emergency_contact_0.cgi">Emergency contact name</a>
<li><a href="field-Patron-Emergency_relationship_0.cgi">Emergency contact relationship</a>
<li><a href="field-Patron-Emergency_phone_0.cgi">Emergency contact phone</a>
<li><a href="field-Patron-Preferences.cgi">Preferences</a>
<li><a href="field_Patron_Cats.cgi">Cats</a>
<li><a href="field_Patron_Dogs.cgi">Dogs</a>
<li><a href="field-Patron-Times receiving.cgi">Times receiving</a>
<li><a href="field_Patron_Note.cgi">Note</a>
<li><a href="field-Patron-Last_seen.cgi">Last seen</a>
<li><a href="field-Patron-Last_seen_by.cgi">Last seen by</a>
<li><a href="field-Patron-Last_route.cgi">Last route</a>
<li><a href="field-Patron-Last_note.cgi">Last note</a>
</ul>
To modify fields you are allowed to modify, click on
<a href="button_Edit.cgi"><button>Edit</button></a>.  Once you have completed any changes,
click on <a href="button-Update.cgi"><button>Update</button></a>.

<p>If you want to add this new patron to your personal contact list, click on
<a href="button_Download_contact.cgi"><button>Download contact</button></a>.
<p>Click <a href="button_larr.cgi"><button>&larr;</button></a> to return to a higher menu.

